snippet.textDisplay:
I am a Bengali, born and brought up in Assam. I did my primary schooling at Shankardev Shishu Niketan. Since my school days, I have had many Assamese friends. Trust me, guys, You are damn lucky if you still meet up with your school friends. 
              I am currently staying in Bengaluru for work, but I deeply miss the Bihus, Pithas, and my childhood friends. I am proud that I was born in Assam. JOI AAI AXOM❤
